<li id="cite_note-Deci.2C_E._1995-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Deci.2C_E._1995_6-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Deci, E. L., &amp; Ryan, R. M. (1995). Human autonomy: The basis for true self-esteem. In M. Kernis (Ed.), <i>Efficacy, agency, and self-esteem</i> (pp.&#160;3149). New York: Plenum.</span></li>
